text: Had the pan seared salmon at Cali Restaurant. It was nicely cooked with a tender center. Flavors were simple but well-balanced. The atmosphere was relaxed and service was friendly. A solid choice if you’re in the area and looking for a decent meal.
really yummy food! my second time back here and will continue to come back. Very unassuming because it is quite quiet at night but it’s very peaceful and good vibes. staff were nice too :) yay

Booked this restaurant from Eatigo and really think it’s worth the 50% off, and we ordered two mains and two side dishes. The steak is cooked evenly and very juicy! The rest of the meal is normal, just alright. There is very little people on Thursday evening. Really love the quiet atmosphere, it is perfect.

Had a dinner with my family here. Great atmosphere with a quiet ambient. I ordered the Pan Seared Salmon, which was well cooked and juicy. A good place to dine in and spend some time with family or friends. Will certainly return and try other food.

I came here twice in a week because I had a great first experience and wanted to bring my friends along. I personally really liked the ribeye. The location is convenient, and the service is good. Will definitely come again!
